The,GitHub,Activity,Watching,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,the,GitHub,repository,watching,feature,into,their,applications,enabling,users,to,receive,notifications,on,new,discussions,This,API,requires,the,user,account,to,be,authenticated,GitHub,is,one,of,the,software,providers,that,specialize,in,a,wide,range,of,application,development